{"id":665098,"date":[{"year":1983,"month":12,"day":13}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"社会大学","column":"","genre":"","count":"166","ytitle":"","mtitle":"莫打扰他","ftitle":"","authors":["罗达成"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"张力钢　摄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗达成　诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一个着迷了，忘了周末，也忘了约会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——整个身心全被知识的琼浆陶醉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一个看呆了，手把门扉，轻轻儿不透"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一点声息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——不是嗔怪，更不是“兴师问罪”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘的眼睛，闪动着三分柔情、七分钦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"佩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑微微，欲语还休，心头别有一种甜滋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"味……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志同道合的爱，岂在这一朝一夕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对!别打扰他，今儿来一个悄然告退。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入8号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1983\\12\\83CD040801.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>张力钢</FONT>"}]}